name: Shit Piss Skin Can
description: Shit Piss Skin Can (SPSC) is a satirical meme coin inspired by an infamous quote from Chase Herro, co-founder of Trump-associated World Liberty Financial. Mr. Herro once said, "You can literally sell shit in a can, wrapped in piss, covered in human skin, for a billion if the story's right, because people will buy it." The token points to the irony of his statement, as a metaphor for cryptocurrency in general.
